<section class="section" data-section-id="{{ section.id }}">
  <h2 class="section-title">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
  <div style="max-width:800px;margin:0 auto">
    <div class="faq-item"><div class="faq-q">What is included in the Sample Kit? <span class="toggle">+</span></div><div class="faq-a">The 20-Color Sample Kit includes real cured bonded stone samples in 20 curated colors, organized in a labeled box.</div></div>
    <div class="faq-item"><div class="faq-q">How long does shipping take? <span class="toggle">+</span></div><div class="faq-a">Sample kits ship to the U.S. in 7–12 business days. You will receive a tracking number once dispatched.</div></div>
    <div class="faq-item"><div class="faq-q">Can I install this myself? <span class="toggle">+</span></div><div class="faq-a">Small areas under 50 sq ft may be suitable for confident DIYers. For larger projects, consult a qualified installer.</div></div>
    <div class="faq-item"><div class="faq-q">How do I order bulk materials? <span class="toggle">+</span></div><div class="faq-a">Bulk material orders are quoted separately. Submit a Project Estimate with your photos and area.</div></div>
    <div class="faq-item"><div class="faq-q">What is your return policy? <span class="toggle">+</span></div><div class="faq-a">Sample kits can be returned unused within 14 days. If damaged, contact us within 48 hours with photos.</div></div>
    <div class="faq-item"><div class="faq-q">Do the colors look the same in person? <span class="toggle">+</span></div><div class="faq-a">Colors may vary depending on lighting. This is why we recommend ordering samples first.</div></div>
    <div class="faq-item"><div class="faq-q">What surfaces can this be applied to? <span class="toggle">+</span></div><div class="faq-a">Bonded stone may be suitable for concrete, asphalt, and stable paver bases depending on condition.</div></div>
    <div class="faq-item"><div class="faq-q">Do you offer contractor referrals? <span class="toggle">+</span></div><div class="faq-a">Yes, we can connect qualified installers in your area.</div></div>
  </div>
</section>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "FAQ Accordion",
  "presets": [{"name": "FAQ Accordion"}]
}
{% endschema %}
